content: tcm390: Merged 18 PRs this week, primarily focused on bug fixes across various components including client auto-scrolling (#3115), image processing (#3056, #3008), and Twitter functionality (#2966, #2951, #2818). Demonstrated consistent daily activity with 71 commits modifying 1726 files (+107k/-28k lines), while also providing 42 code reviews (35 approvals) and contributing to 26 issue discussions. Notable contributions include fixing message ID collisions in Telegram Client (#3053, +942/-267) and adding Twitter post media functionality (#2818, +1389/-161).
